      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# Redis Enterprise Shard Dashboard\n\nThe metrics tracked in this dashboard relate to shard level metrics. Shards are the lowest single unit you can will be tracking in Redis Enterprise. In this dashboard you can track bits such as CPU Utilization, Memory, Key Counts, number of connections as well as fragmentation, you can drill down to all the shards on a cluster, all the shards on a single database, all the shards on a node, or even just a single shard to inspect what's going on at the shard level."
